Project Overview

Luxury Split Showcase is a premium custom section built for Shopify themes using Liquid, HTML, and CSS. This section is designed to create a luxury storytelling experience by combining sticky sidebar navigation with visually rich content blocks.

The left panel remains fixed while users explore multiple featured collections, campaigns, or brand stories on the right side through smooth scrolling interactions.

Features

✅ Sticky sidebar navigation
✅ Dynamic block-based content management
✅ Merchant-friendly theme customization
✅ Large responsive image rendering
✅ Hover zoom animations
✅ Smooth content browsing experience
✅ Mobile and tablet optimized layout
✅ Clean and scalable section architecture

